sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor B as Buyer
    participant MB as MagicBricks
    participant GM as Broker's Gmail
    participant IN as Brokly Ingest
    participant AI as Gemini
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant WA as WhatsApp Cloud API
    actor BR as Broker (Arnav)

    B->>MB: Taps "Contact Agent" on the 3BHK listing
    MB->>GM: Lead email — buyer name, phone, listing ref
    GM->>IN: Auto-forward to arnav-4821@leads.brokly.in
    IN->>AI: Extract buyer · phone · portal · property
    AI-->>IN: Structured lead JSON
    IN->>DB: Match listing, or auto-create the card
    IN->>DB: Upsert lead (dedupe by phone) + AI score
    DB-->>BR: Dashboard card pops live (Realtime)
    IN->>WA: Alert the broker
    WA->>BR: New MagicBricks lead — Rahul · 3BHK Whitefield
    IN->>WA: First-touch utility template to buyer
    WA->>B: You enquired about 3BHK Whitefield — full details on the Brokly link
    B->>WA: Buyer replies — 24h free window opens
    WA->>IN: Webhook — buyer bot Q&A / broker inbox
    Note over B,BR: Every message after this lives on WhatsApp + Brokly links — the portal is never needed again
